arget=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important;=
 border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-styl=
e: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> here</a> about potential remedies in th=
is case. The short version is that if the judge concludes that Musk has no =
right to terminate the merger agreement, then she can either make him pay $=
